Description
-----------

Ignore the [fragment
program](Vertex_and_fragment_programs "Vertex and fragment programs")
extension.

Usage
-----

At the console type...

    r_inhibitFragmentProgram [boolean]

Parameters
----------

-   [boolean]
    -   0 - Use the best possible quality setting.
    -   1 - Don't use any fragment programs.

